{"tid":1370824,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[機會]港鐵車長實名聯署- 反擊資本家與偽建制","createTime":"2019-07-27T06:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T01:00:40.000Z","uid":110892,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ba258ef285ea81545e64cf528e20291caa64e9b8","tid":1370824,"uid":110892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T06:08:23.000Z","msg":"其實港鐵車長實名聯署係一個好好嘅機會去籌組鐵路工會，然後各行各業順勢籌組各種聯合工會，挑戰香港資本家一直以來的霸權。<br />\n<br />\n咁樣，嗰啲一直口講為全力支持政府與本地資本家角力而推出既任何施政，但事實上只係另一批資本家既走狗，冇藉口再支持政府，亦再無「本地資本家」呢個「假想敵」。<br />\n<br />\n政府成日話打走資本霸權，拯救香港，但其實只係將令一批資本換血。<br />\n<br />\n真正幫到香港既，係建立健全勞工權益制度。<br />\n<br />\n打資本霸權並唔係靠政權，係直接從勞工團體出招。<br />\n<br />\n真普選可能係中央決定，但勞工事務絕對係香港內部事務，用勞工組織間接影響政府施政，<span style=\"color: red;\">無得輸</span><br />\n<br />\n自此，政府再無得幻想自己係正義一方對抗地產商<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">建立工會</span>"},{"pid":"c39c02e84b72aa5e811658e198121ac6c22efbef","tid":1370824,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T06:10:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"245a9614bd96daee26e3baa7de2b3c1554935c71","tid":1370824,"uid":110892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T06:11:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68887b6ff80954a251e96ae10d0015c4632d7008","tid":1370824,"uid":110892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:31:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9589cb39127233403c4b20a33977e4dcdaca9132","tid":1370824,"uid":110892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:37:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d66a66da8e144bc238c5bd1c681e588fd1ff3226","tid":1370824,"uid":110892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:41:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfd5d664121a36861e0c949a36f01fc62f146a2b","tid":1370824,"uid":91631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:53:12.000Z","msg":"好認同<br />\n根本要大罷工就唔係一個行業一個職業既事<br />\n自己做緊個行都唔去組織工會搞罷工<br />\n好意思剩係叫車長出黎罷工，<br />\n跟住打去同老闆講：「我唔係罷工，不過車長唔返工，要怪就怪車長。」咁樣呀？<br />\n功就大家領，鑊就你食<br />\n依家個觀感就係咁。"},{"pid":"af1287d8bde37ce5ad9eb6a85628121e1a14ea09","tid":1370824,"uid":253954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:18:07.000Z","msg":"如果九巴都擺就好玩"},{"pid":"163d14727a260c9cbb466dac663771d370618e92","tid":1370824,"uid":110892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:15:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04789e5684e278a277588974f8613c214d902e0f","tid":1370824,"uid":110892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:00:40.000Z","msg":"最後一推"}]}